import React from 'react';
import { Box, Typography, Link, Grid, Divider } from '@mui/material';
import { styled } from '@mui/system';

const StyledFooter = styled(Box)({
  backgroundColor: '#000000',
  color: '#ffffff',
  padding: '40px 20px',
  width: '100%',
  bottom: 0,
});

const FooterLink = styled(Link)({
  color: '#ffffff',
  textDecoration: 'none',
  transition: 'color 0.3s ease',
  '&:hover': {
    color: '#28b463',
  },
});

const FooterSectionTitle = styled(Typography)({
  color: '#ffffff',
  fontWeight: 'bold',
  marginBottom: '15px',
  fontSize: '1.1rem',
});

const SocialIcon = styled(Link)({
  color: '#ffffff',
  margin: '0 10px',
  fontSize: '1.5rem',
  transition: 'color 0.3s ease',
  '&:hover': {
    color: '#28b463',
  },
});

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <StyledFooter component="footer">
      <Grid container spacing={4} justifyContent="center">
        {/* Company Info Section */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <FooterSectionTitle variant="h6">Baa M Boo</FooterSectionTitle>
          <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
            Premium Oversized Tees for Men & Women
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body2">
            Quality apparel designed for comfort and style.
            Cash on Delivery available across India.
          </Typography>
        </Grid>

        {/* Quick Links Section */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <FooterSectionTitle variant="h6">Quick Links</FooterSectionTitle>
          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 1 }}>
            <FooterLink href="#home">Home</FooterLink>
            <FooterLink href="#shop">Shop</FooterLink>
            <FooterLink href="#about">About Us</FooterLink>
            <FooterLink href="#faq">FAQ</FooterLink>
            <FooterLink href="#returns">Returns & Refunds</FooterLink>
          </Box>
        </Grid>

        {/* Support Section */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <FooterSectionTitle variant="h6">Support</FooterSectionTitle>
          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 1 }}>
            <FooterLink href="#contact">Contact Us</FooterLink>
            <FooterLink href="#privacy">Privacy Policy</FooterLink>
            <FooterLink href="#terms">Terms of Service</FooterLink>
            <FooterLink href="#shipping">Shipping Policy</FooterLink>
            <FooterLink href="mailto:support@baamboo.com">
              support@baamboo.com
            </FooterLink>
          </Box>
        </Grid>

        {/* Connect Section */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <FooterSectionTitle variant="h6">Connect With Us</FooterSectionTitle>
          <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
            Follow us for updates and exclusive offers:
          </Typography>
          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', gap: 1 }}>
            <SocialIcon href="https://facebook.com/baamboo" target="_blank">
              <i className="fab fa-facebook-f" />
            </SocialIcon>
            <SocialIcon href="https://instagram.com/baamboo" target="_blank">
              <i className="fab fa-instagram" />
            </SocialIcon>
            <SocialIcon href="https://twitter.com/baamboo" target="_blank">
              <i className="fab fa-twitter" />
            </SocialIcon>
            <SocialIcon href="https://pinterest.com/baamboo" target="_blank">
              <i className="fab fa-pinterest" />
            </SocialIcon>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>

      {/* Newsletter Subscription */}
      <Box sx={{ mt: 4, textAlign: 'center' }}>
        <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
          Stay Updated
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
          Subscribe to our newsletter for exclusive deals and updates.
        </Typography>
        <Box
          component="form"
          sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', gap: 1, maxWidth: '400px', mx: 'auto' }}
        >
          <input
            type="email"
            placeholder="Enter your email"
            style={{
              padding: '10px',
              borderRadius: '4px',
              border: 'none',
              width: '70%',
            }}
          />
          <button
            type="submit"
            style={{
              padding: '10px 20px',
              backgroundColor: '#28b463',
              color: '#ffffff',
              border: 'none',
              borderRadius: '4px',
              cursor: 'pointer',
              transition: 'background-color 0.3s ease',
            }}
            onMouseOver={(e) => (e.target.style.backgroundColor = '#229954')}
            onMouseOut={(e) => (e.target.style.backgroundColor = '#28b463')}
          >
            Subscribe
          </button>
        </Box>
      </Box>

      {/* Divider */}
      <Divider sx={{ my: 4, backgroundColor: '#ffffff33' }} />

      {/* Copyright Section */}
      <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
        <Typography variant="caption">
          Â© 2025 Baa M Boo. All rights reserved.
        </Typography>
      </Box>
    </StyledFooter>
  );
};

export default Footer;
